[[Kaplan University]] is a [[University of Phoenix]] [[masturbation|knock-off]], for the strong-willed, energetic intellectuals out there.

Their advertising campaign really hits home -- pages filled with stock photos of tramps you will never get to nail aside from a swazy on [[Second Life]].

